"     <a class=\"nounderline abstract\" href=\"mobipreview.htm?30/39/31348/abstract/5\">",
"      Mukherjee A, Murray RD, Columb B, et al. Acquired prolactin deficiency indicates severe hypopituitarism in patients with disease of the hypothalamic-pituitary axis. Clin Endocrinol (Oxf) 2003; 59:743.",
