" <div class=\"graphic\">",
"  <div class=\"figure\" style=\"width: 524px\">",
"   <div class=\"ttl\">",
"    Mild dyshidrotic eczema",
"   </div>",
"   <div class=\"cntnt\" style=\"width: 504px; height: 378px; background-image: url(data:image/jpeg;base64,);\">",
"   </div>",
"   <div class=\"lgnd\">",
"    Mild forms of dyshidrotic eczema are clinically characterized by a small number of vesicles and mild erythema and desquamation.",
